    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Prepare to be amazed by this absolute showstopper! This vehicle is in pristine, mint condition and looks like it just rolled off the showroom floor. From its flawless exterior to its immaculate interior, every detail has been perfectly preserved, making it a dream find for any collector or serious enthusiast. It drives as beautifully as it looks\u2014don't miss your chance to own a truly exceptional piece of automotive excellence!",
